data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch style home featuring an upstairs bonus room with an additional bedroom and full bathroom. Situated on a corner lot, this property boasts a bright and inviting atmosphere, complemented by a fantastic floor plan and fenced backyard. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that fills the spacious living areas. The open layout seamlessly connects the living room, dining area and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining friends and family. The beautiful kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, ample counter space, convenient center island and custom shelving in pantry. The master suite is a true sanctuary, with sitting room that opens to covered back porch, and a generous size walk-in custom closet. Bathroom features a large tile shower with separate vanities, for ultimate relaxation and rejuvenation. Additional main floor bedrooms offer comfort and privacy. Additionally, the upstairs bonus room provides endless possibilities, whether it be a home office, media room, or play area. Subdivision has exceptional amenities! Easy access to 400 and new Cumming City Center, Greenway, Halcyon and tons of shopping! Schedule your showing today!
